# Page Object Model Directory

This directory contains Page Object Model classes for E2E tests.

## Base Classes

- `base-page.ts` - Abstract base class with common functionality

## Page Objects

Create page objects for each major page/feature:
- `login-page.ts` - Login page interactions
- `dashboard-page.ts` - Dashboard page interactions
- etc.

## Usage

```typescript
import { BasePage } from './base-page'

class MyPage extends BasePage {
  // Page-specific methods
}
```
